Package org.osmdroid.api

Interface Summary
IGeoPoint An interface that resembles the Google Maps API GeoPoint class and is implemented by the osmdroid GeoPoint class.
IMapController An interface that resembles the Google Maps API MapController class and is implemented by the osmdroid MapController class.
IMapView An interface that resembles the Google Maps API MapView class and is implemented by the osmdroid MapView class.
IMyLocationOverlay An interface that resembles the Google Maps API MyLocationOverlay class and is implemented by the osmdroid MyLocationOverlay class.
IProjection An interface that resembles the Google Maps API Projection interface and is implemented by the osmdroid MapView.Projection class.
